Your computeQpJacobian looks fine but you also need a computeQpOffDiagJacobian term for your potential variable.
Real
NernstElec::computeQpOffDiagJacobian(unsigned int jvar)
{
  if (jvar == _elec_var)
    return _elec_cond[_qp] * _grad_test[_i][_qp] * _u[_qp] * _grad_phi[_j][_qp];
  else
    return 0;
}
